types.html:
diversifié (feminine diversifiée, masculine plural diversifiés, feminine plural diversifiées)

  1. modified by diversification
  2. diverse, composed of people with a variety of different demographic characteristics in terms of, for example, ethnicity, gender, sexual orientation, socioeconomic status, etc.
trans: diverse, composed of people with a variety of different demographic characteristics in terms of, for example, ethnicity, gender, sexual orientation, socioeconomic status, etc.
